  "rationale": "Designed using Finsweet's 6-layer Client-First logic to ensure maximum scalability and clarity. Built from scratch with Div Blocks to avoid 'w-nav' limitations and ensure 100% control over naming conventions as per MAS-DS-001. All spacing, dimensions, and typography are defined in 'rem' to ensure fluid responsiveness and accessibility. Styles are mapped to existing Webflow variables identified in the design system audit (e.g., color--primary, color--text-active) to maintain architectural integrity."
